title: D3_MC_Start1
---
<<bg corridor>>
The hallway is already busy before the first lesson. Lockers slam shut, people greet their friends, and the usual morning chaos fills the corridor.

You’re heading toward your classroom when a familiar voice stops you.

<<SetMood "Bebe neutral">>
Bebe: Well, if it isn’t Cassie’s new favorite person.

{$playerName}: That’s a bold claim this early in the morning.

Bebe: Please. Cassie talked about you enough yesterday.
Bebe: I figured I should say hi before she drags you away again.

{$playerName}: Is that jealousy I’m hearing?

Bebe raises an eyebrow.

Bebe: Careful, {$playerName}. Flirting with me this early might ruin your reputation.

{$playerName}: I didn’t know I had one.

Bebe: You do now.
Bebe: So tell me something. Are you always this charming, or are you just trying to impress me?

-> (Plus Bebe) Maybe a little of both
    {$playerName}: Maybe a little of both.
    Bebe laughs softly.
    Bebe: Bold answer. I respect it.
-> (Neutral) I'm just being myself
    {$playerName}: I’m just being myself.
    Bebe shrugs.
    Bebe: Fair enough. Guess we’ll see how long that lasts here.

<<SetMood "Bebe hide">>
<<SetMood "Kase neutral">>
Kase: There you are.

{$playerName}: Morning.

Kase: Morning.

<<SetMood "Kase hide">>
<<SetMood "Bebe neutral">>
Bebe: We were just talking.

<<SetMood "Bebe hide">>
<<SetMood "Kase neutral">>
Kase: Uh huh. That what we’re calling it?

<<SetMood "Kase hide">>
<<SetMood "Bebe neutral">>
Bebe: Don’t start.

The warning bell rings.

<<SetMood "Bebe hide">>
<<SetMood "Kase neutral">>
Kase: That’s our cue.

<<SetMood "Kase hide">>
<<SetMood "Bebe neutral">>
Bebe: See you later, {$playerName}.

<<SetMood "Bebe hide">>

You continue toward class.
<<jump D3_C_Classroom1>>
===

title: D3_C_Classroom1
---
<<bg classroom>>

Across the room Cassie notices you approaching.

<<SetMood "Cassie happy">>
Cassie: Hey! You made it on time.

{$playerName}: I’ve got the hang of this place… mostly.

Cassie giggles.

Cassie: “Mostly” sounds promising.
Cassie: So… did you figure out what you want for the school trip?

-> (Neutral) Hmm… I was thinking the mountains.
    {$playerName}: Hmm… I was thinking the mountains.
    Cassie pouts playfully.
    Cassie: I see how it is… trying to make me leave the city behind!
-> (Plus Cassie) The city trip sounds great.
    {$playerName}: The city trip sounds great.
    Cassie beams.
    Cassie: Right?! Museums, cafes… it sounds amazing!

The teacher begins the lesson.

<<SetMood "Cassie hide">>

<<bg corridor>>

You spot Emiko sneaking out near the gym. Her eyes meet yours before she quickly joins you.
      <<SetMood "Emiko neutral">>
Emiko: Hey, want to skip for a bit? We could hang out outside if you like.
    -> (+ for Emiko) Sure, lead the way.
        <<jump D3_Emiko_Positive1>>
    -> (Neutral) Sorry, maybe next time.
        <<jump D3_Emiko_Negative1>>
===

title: D3_Emiko_Positive1
---
{$playerName}: Sure, lead the way.
      <<SetMood "Emiko happy">>
Emiko: Thanks… I wasn’t sure if anyone would notice.
{$playerName}: You could say I’m observant. Or maybe I just like sneaking around with you.
      <<SetMood "Emiko blush">>
Emiko: *laughs softly* You’re weird… but not in a bad way.
You find a quiet spot outside the school, where the sun hits just right on the benches by the trees. You sit together, chatting about school, hobbies, and random funny things that happened over the past week.
{$playerName}: You know… you look a lot better when you’re not hiding from everyone.
      <<SetMood "Emiko blush">>
Emiko: *blushing* Stop it… you’re making me… uh… I mean, I’m fine!
The conversation continues, light and playful, and you feel a connection forming as the minutes pass by. It’s calm, fun, and maybe… a little flirty.
      <<SetMood "Emiko happy">>
Emiko: I’m glad you came with me.
{$playerName}: Me too.
The bell rings, signaling it’s time to head back. You both stand up, linking arms briefly as you make your way back toward class.
      <<SetMood "Emiko hide">>
 <<jump D3_S_Gym1>>
===

title: D3_Emiko_Negative1
---
{$playerName}: Sorry, maybe next time.
      <<SetMood "Emiko neutral">>
Emiko’s smile falters slightly, but she nods.
Emiko: Yeah… okay. See you later, then.
      <<SetMood "Emiko hide">>
You watch her head back toward the gym before you continue to your own class.
 <<jump D3_S_Gym1>>
