title: D3_S_Gym1
---
<<bg gymnasium>>

    <<SetMood "Teacher neutral">>
Teacher: Alright everyone, pick a side! Blue team or red team!
You glance around. Sasha is warming up near one side, bouncing a basketball effortlessly.
-> (+ for Sasha) Join the blue team
        <<SetMood "Teacher hide">>
        <<SetMood "Sasha neutral">>
        You head over to the blue team, and Sasha immediately spots you.
        Sasha: Finally! Don’t let me carry the team alone.
        {$playerName}: Wouldn’t dream of it.
        <<SetMood "Sasha happy">>
        The game starts, and you pass, dribble, and shoot alongside her. Sasha is competitive but playful, teasing you every time you miss a shot. Her energy is infectious, and you find yourself keeping pace with her.
        Sasha: Not bad… you might actually be useful.
        {$playerName}: Only because you make it fun.
        The game ends with your team winning. Blue team cheers, Sasha laughs, and high-fives you before running off to grab a water bottle.
        Sasha: That was awesome. We should do that again sometime.
-> (+ for Takiko) Join the red team
    <<SetMood "Teacher hide">>
    <<SetMood "Takiko neutral">>
    You join the red team, opposite Sasha. The game starts fast.
    Sasha: You’re on my side of the court now? Fine. I won’t go easy.
    {$playerName}: That’s… terrifying.
    <<SetMood "Takiko hide">>
    <<SetMood "Sasha angry">>
    She dribbles, sprinting past you. When you try to block her, her elbow accidentally hits your side, and you stumble.
    {$playerName}: *groaning* Ow…
    <<SetMood "Sasha hide">>
    <<SetMood "Takiko neutral">>
    Takiko, supervising nearby, notices immediately and strides over.
    Takiko: Hey! Are you okay?
    {$playerName}: I… think I got hit.
    Takiko: *sighs* Figures you’d get yourself hurt. Come on, I’ll take you to the infirmary.
    She helps you up, supporting your weight, and you make a show of leaning slightly closer than necessary.
    {$playerName}: You know… you make falling look like less of a punishment.
    Takiko: *snorts* Don’t get any ideas. I’m not babysitting you for your flirting.
    {$playerName}: *grinning* Flirting or not, I’d say it’s working.
<<SetMood "Sasha hide">>
<<SetMood "Takiko hide">>
<<jump D3_MC_Cafeteria1>>
===

title: D3_MC_Cafeteria1
---
<<bg cafeteria>>
The lunch bell rings, and the cafeteria is buzzing with activity. Students line up for food, laughing and joking, trays clattering. You grab your tray and look around for somewhere to sit.
Your eyes scan the room and you spot a few familiar faces.
    <<SetMood "Bebe hide">>
Bebe, sitting with Cassie and Kase, waving at you. 
    <<SetMood "Cassie hide">>
Cassie waves excitedly.
    <<SetMood "Sasha hide">>
Sasha, already surrounded by her basketball friends, laughing loudly.
    <<SetMood "Nancy hide">>
A quieter table near the library entrance where Nancy, the student council vice president, sits with some papers, looking organized and approachable.

{$playerName} (thought): Hmm… who should I sit with today?

-> A. Join Bebe and Cassie
    <<jump D3_Lunch_Bebe>>
-> B. Join Sasha
    <<jump D3_Lunch_Sasha>>
-> C. Join Nancy
    <<jump D3_Lunch_Nancy>>

===

