title: D3_MC_Lab1
---
<<bg classroom>>

Students enter chemistry lab.

<<SetMood "Teacher neutral">>
Teacher: Partner lab today!

<<SetMood "Teacher hide">>

You look around.

Nancy reviewing notes.
Takiko standing confidently.
Emiko by the window.

Who do you partner with?
    -> Nancy
        <<SetMood "Nancy neutral">>
        You approach Nancy.
        {$playerName}: Hey, mind if I partner with you?
        Nancy: *glances up, slightly surprised* Oh… sure. I suppose working together could be… efficient.
        {$playerName}: Efficient, huh? Sounds like a perfect excuse to spend time with the smartest girl in class.
        Nancy’s cheeks tint pink, and she clears her throat.
        Nancy: Don’t push your luck, Mc. But… try not to mess up the experiment, okay?
        You both set up your materials. As you work, you exchange ideas and joke lightly, with Nancy occasionally teasing you about small mistakes while secretly enjoying your presence.

        <<SetMood "Nancy hide">>
    -> Takiko
        <<SetMood "Takiko neutral">>
        You walk over to Takiko.
        {$playerName}: Mind if I join you for this lab?
        Takiko: *crossing her arms, smirking* Hah… you sure you can keep up? I don’t go easy on partners.
        {$playerName}: *grinning* Good. I like a challenge.
        Takiko: *narrows her eyes, flustered just slightly* Don’t get cocky…
        As you work together, Takiko’s competitive side comes out—she corrects you, measures carefully, and tries to push you to do better, all while her cheeks tint slightly whenever you tease her.
        {$playerName}: Don’t worry, I can handle being bossed around… especially by someone as intense as you.
        Takiko: *blushes faintly, turning away* I-I’m not intense!
        The lab continues with playful tension as you both carefully complete the experiment, her tsundere personality keeping things lively.

        <<SetMood "Takiko hide">>
    -> Emiko
        <<SetMood "Emiko happy">>
        You walk over to Emiko.
        {$playerName}: Hey… want to partner up for this lab?
        Emiko: *smiles softly* Sure! That’d be nice.
        {$playerName}: You know, working with you might just make chemistry my favorite subject.
        Emiko blushes faintly and laughs.
        Emiko: *shyly* You’re… such a goof sometimes…
        As you set up your materials, you and Emiko chat quietly, laughing softly whenever one of you makes a small mistake. The mood is calm, light, and playful, letting you bond naturally.
        {$playerName} (thought): This is… nice. Feels like it’s just the two of us here.

        <<SetMood "Emiko hide">>

The teacher walks around, checking each group’s progress. 
The class hums with quiet conversation, laughter, and the occasional hiss of the burners.
The bell rings, and students start packing up. You feel a little closer to your partner as you head to your next class.

<<NextDay>>

